Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.47,0:00:03.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1500,0)}-3天过去了-
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.73,0:00:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.11,0:00:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么地方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.62,0:00:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保健室
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.16,0:00:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保健室？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.40,0:00:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们为什么还在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.56,0:00:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要勉强自己
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.23,0:00:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不要紧 小奏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.48,0:00:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小百合真是辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.71,0:00:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真亏你能担任首领
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.15,0:00:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,连你们都在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.93,0:00:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.92,0:00:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,影子不是已经消失了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.99,0:00:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就不会有妨碍你们的东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.47,0:00:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.30,0:00:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.50,0:00:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是还在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.06,0:01:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还留在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.01,0:01:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.97,0:01:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.76,0:01:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.72,0:01:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.00,0:01:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不确定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.85,0:01:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但百合的心结可能已经解开了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.40,0:01:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗 百合
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.72,0:01:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎 呃 那个 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.92,0:01:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 让我用催眠术让你坦白…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.33,0:01:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快住手 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.02,0:01:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看她不情愿的态度
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.26,0:01:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是说中了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.21,0:01:33.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 没有这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.33,0:01:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可是首领
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.59,0:01:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么容易就解开了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.12,0:01:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,岂不是惹人笑话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.26,0:01:38.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.84,0:01:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就用催眠术…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.63,0:01:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错 是解开了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.97,0:01:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有意见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.49,0:01:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 承认了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.96,0:01:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小奏你好坏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.71,0:01:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是百合喜欢闹别扭罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.12,0:01:56.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还真敢说
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.80,0:02:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过 我还蛮开心的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.74,0:02:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.11,0:02:03.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为你叫我百合了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.31,0:02:05.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.43,0:02:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为 就像朋友一样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.13,0:02:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.62,0:02:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.92,0:02:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么说 我们的准备没有白费咯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.55,0:02:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.59,0:02:17.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,准备？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.79,0:02:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要做什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.72,0:02:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最后有件想做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.22,0:02:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奏说她还没做过
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.06,0:02:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？ 什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.66,0:02:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimSun\bord0\1c&H000000&\fs100\pos(640,680)}毕业
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.22,0:02:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其他人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.60,0:02:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全都走了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.02,0:02:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.29,0:02:37.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多亏有大家帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.45,0:02:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然也费了不少事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.05,0:02:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哼 那是神技
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.99,0:02:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然嘴上不承认
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.12,0:02:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但大家还蛮享受这边的生活的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.24,0:02:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我明白了这个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.86,0:02:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这也多亏了小百合
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.38,0:02:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.23,0:02:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 高松也走了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.56,0:02:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然变成了NPC 但恢复意识了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.61,0:02:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎 这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.75,0:03:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不怎么吃惊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.03,0:03:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是说变成NPC就没法恢复了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.57,0:03:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来设定成了凭借强大意志
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.13,0:03:09.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天能变回人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.85,0:03:16.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这首歌是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.50,0:03:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚才工作时也在唱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.00,0:03:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是什么来着
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.81,0:03:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是那首吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.25,0:03:25.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,岩泽最后唱的那首
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.00,0:03:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My song
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.26,0:03:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那首歌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.74,0:03:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全校广播的那首吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.32,0:03:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.81,0:03:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是首好歌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.32,0:03:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.15,0:03:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,体育馆？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.30,0:03:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.45,0:03:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\1c&H000000&\bord0\pos(640,591)}死后世界战线 毕业典礼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.21,0:03:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是我们做的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.03,0:03:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,字是奏负责
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.58,0:03:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.37,0:03:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小奏 你没毕过业啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.92,0:03:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想会很有趣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.09,0:04:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一点意思都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.71,0:04:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你写字时还蛮开心的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.17,0:04:07.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女生大都会哭哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.54,0:04:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哼 所以说女人这东西…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.09,0:04:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么 开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.28,0:04:14.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在就开始吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.59,0:04:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以为换衣服是为了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.57,0:04:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.88,0:04:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想真会消失吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.53,0:04:21.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还没做好思想准备…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.16,0:04:24.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么 这也算是原首领吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.99,0:04:25.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.19,0:04:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感觉大家消失后 你就没有领袖的样子了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.07,0:04:32.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.55,0:04:34.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,确实有什么变了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.23,0:04:35.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.33,0:04:37.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.47,0:04:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感觉像个女孩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.62,0:04:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我应该高兴吗 还是应该发火？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.86,0:04:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,战斗结束后 变回连这个都不知道的天真女孩了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.57,0:04:51.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小百合也有可爱的地方嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.26,0:04:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 笨蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.03,0:04:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.11,0:04:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,百合真有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.51,0:05:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.70,0:05:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,致开幕词
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.69,0:05:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在举行在死后世界战斗至今的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.55,0:05:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死后世界战线毕业典礼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.11,0:05:14.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,首先 齐唱战歌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.91,0:05:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,战歌？ 那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.40,0:05:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死后世界战线的歌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.54,0:05:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算是代替校歌了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.83,0:05:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可不记得有让人写过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.90,0:05:26.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那也是奏写的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.65,0:05:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你写的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.18,0:05:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,话说你根本不是战线成员吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.92,0:05:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这有什么不好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.31,0:05:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 传一下歌词
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.53,0:05:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,旋律呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.17,0:05:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,校歌都差不多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.99,0:05:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,随便唱一下就好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.11,0:05:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.02,0:05:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一二
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.36,0:05:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从天上的死后战线
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.55,0:05:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由闲人成员
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.58,0:05:52.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为您广播
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.85,0:05:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死前一定要试吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.36,0:06:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻婆豆腐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.12,0:06:05.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 麻婆豆腐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.03,0:06:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻婆豆腐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.98,0:06:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是哪门子歌词啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.54,0:06:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁来事先检查一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.09,0:06:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真会唱出来耶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.38,0:06:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小奏也是费了好一番工夫写出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.87,0:06:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要说得这么过分嘛 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.24,0:06:23.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,写的认真吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.86,0:06:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这上面不是写着“闲人”吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.86,0:06:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但该怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.50,0:06:31.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感觉字里行间饱含着奏的感情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.10,0:06:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.67,0:06:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从头到尾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.86,0:06:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.70,0:06:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 小奏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.42,0:06:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.96,0:06:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.14,0:06:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,颁发毕业证书
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.99,0:06:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.11,0:06:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.89,0:06:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也基本是奏做的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.76,0:06:56.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么 颁发证书的校长呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.93,0:06:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.42,0:07:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 是我猜拳输了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.96,0:07:07.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有意见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.11,0:07:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 为什么总是我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.36,0:07:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}因为由你做最合适
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.08,0:07:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.96,0:07:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,颁发毕业证书
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.06,0:07:24.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么 立华奏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.97,0:07:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.70,0:07:53.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下一个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.59,0:07:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仲村百合
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.92,0:07:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.28,0:08:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这副打扮很合适你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.19,0:08:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要你管
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.13,0:08:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H000000&\bord0\frz3\move(1012,387,1035,337)}毕\N业\N证\N书
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.13,0:08:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H000000&\bord0\frz4\move(789,560,812,510)}仲\N村\N百\N合\N同\N学
